                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant K</hi> 31.) I was at the station-house when the prisoner was brought in—I assisted to search him. and found a crown, six half-crowns, sixteen shillings, two sixpences, one four-penny piece, and 5 3/4 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>. in copper—he said to Mr. Vincent, "If I gave you a bad half-sovereign, I was in your house quite long enough for you to discover it—I produce the bad half-sovereign I got from Mr. Vinacent.</p>
